- flash.each do |type, message|
  javascript:
    $.growl({
      message: "#{{message}}",
      type: "#{new_flash_class_for type}",
      delay: 10000,
      mouse_over: 'pause',
      offset: {
        x: 0,
        y: 0
      },
      animate: {
        enter: 'animated fadeInRightBig',
        exit: 'animated fadeOutRightBig'
      }
    })

- if !resource.blank? and !resource.errors.blank?
  / Full_messages only have messages, no type
  - resource.errors.full_messages.each do |message|
    javascript:
      $.growl({
        message: "#{{message}}",
        type: 'warning',
        delay: 10000,
        mouse_over: 'pause',
        offset: {
          x: 0,
          y: 0
        },
        animate: {
          enter: 'animated fadeInRightBig',
          exit: 'animated fadeOutRightBig'
        }
      })
